                <p>The best features you can find in a site all in one.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                    <div class="bg-white text-center h-100 p-4 p-xl-5">
                        <img class="img-fluid mb-4" src="~/img/icon-1.png" alt="">
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Lots of trucks</h4>
                        <p class="mb-4">Our catalogue is full with all kinds of trucks.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                    <div class="bg-white text-center h-100 p-4 p-xl-5">
                        <img class="img-fluid mb-4" src="~/img/icon-2.png" alt="">
                        <h4 class="mb-3">Good description</h4>
                        <p class="mb-4">The best description of a truck youll ever see.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
                    <div class="bg-white text-center h-100 p-4 p-xl-5">
                        <img class="img-fluid mb-4" src="~/img/icon-3.png" alt="">
                        <h4 class="mb-3">24/7 support</h4>
                        <p class="mb-4">kind and allways responsive team ready to help you out.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
